{"tid":115275,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚引玉]求京阪神美食推介","createTime":"2017-02-10T12:33:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T10:50:23.000Z","uid":18394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9943da625987d900c5adbfd7b1c4cb533f3ba640","tid":115275,"uid":18394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:33:10.000Z","msg":"黎緊會去關西 所以想集思一下大阪京都神戶有咩美食推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知飛田好多正野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但想集中講食落肚個d 先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下面有我個人推介 希望引到玉啦<br />\n<br />\n1. 和牛　まつした<br />\n呢間係上次去大阪時特登book ge 一間餐廳 專食和牛 簡佢原因係當時tabelog見到都幾高分<br />\n間野位唔多 最好拜託日本朋友/酒店幫你book 定<br />\n上次去食發現大部分都係本地人 旅客幾乎係零 <br />\n個次叫左個set dinner 人頭費每人一萬羊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貴係貴 但質數好好 食法有燒肉有他他有壽司等等<br />\n和牛脂肪勁多 呢一餐基本上係飽到落腳趾尾<br />\n最後間野係梅田 都幾難搵 因為google 都會帶錯你路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/10/200206_2bd9a479aa4e1ccf6159b6a2e45ef196.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F10%2F200206_2bd9a479aa4e1ccf6159b6a2e45ef196.jpg&h=0e0cbc32&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/10/200209_362634ce654f38484e30a93e1b2d62e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F10%2F200209_362634ce654f38484e30a93e1b2d62e4.jpg&h=a84134c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/10/200212_a6a78c2a610cb892071f028bcf731719.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F10%2F200212_a6a78c2a610cb892071f028bcf731719.jpg&h=84f99aac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.網元<br />\n呢間係舊登睇post 介紹 係蟹道樂姐妹店黎 但比蟹道樂舒服勁多 我建議去食lunch 會比較抵d <br />\n我上次係去食本館 鋪面已經超靚同蟹道樂冇得比 但注意本館lunch 只做星期六日 <br />\n入到去係比左一間房我地 我上次4個人去係3個人service我地 勁癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食物方面係一道道上 上之前會有人同你講上緊邊道 食物就不過不失 食哂成餐男仔應該唔會夠飽 個人覺得重頭戲係最後個甜品 佢會比你簡要咩味 如果你簡左抺茶味 佢會有個阿姨跪係度做茶道再淋落雪糕度 <br />\n總結呢間野我覺得淨係服務呢點已經值哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大阪有好幾間分店 位置都好就腳嫁！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/10/203115_06bf9ce58110a4e10c3c61ddf1a57193.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F10%2F203115_06bf9ce58110a4e10c3c61ddf1a57193.jpg&h=23fdbfd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3O04eX3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3O04eX3.jpg&h=6168e777&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dqW94Gz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdqW94Gz.jpg&h=5a121625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.力丸燒肉<br />\n呢間唔洗講 旅遊書都大推 主要係因為任食 抵 質數好<br />\n放題形式 任嗌嫁喎 咁ge 價錢黎講d 肉真係好高質 入面會有中文menu 所以唔怕唔識睇 <br />\n同埋最重要一點係佢係用炭爐燒烤 燒出黎同平時電爐係兩樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過正正因為係炭燒 缺點就係好搶火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但間鋪都會比碗冰你去整熄d 火<br />\n另一缺點就係鋪頭通風系統做得唔好 食完一餐成身油煙味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢間都係好多分店 亦都好就腳 心齋橋已經有幾間 大家可以去試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/182N7sw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F182N7sw.jpg&h=a7a54bf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下次旅程黎緊會去試<br />\n法貴-神戶牛(見有巴打係post 推介 就book 左位去試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n漁伊/宇奈とと-鰻魚飯 (一間平價一間貴少少 但大家都係天神橋 應該到時會再決定食邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n拋完磚希望有巴絲引下玉 如果地點就腳可能會去一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果返黎發掘到有咩正野 應該會打返篇遊記(希望出到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"721c18e5bda37d55668d5f5d2dd0f35d70e7066d","tid":115275,"uid":12370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:36:15.000Z","msg":"去大阪都係食松屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其餘瘋狂飛田松島尼崎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0ca8b3cbbf16115a9de61759e2cdf38465dd0f","tid":115275,"uid":21624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:37:06.000Z","msg":"京都 大久保 <br />\n食沾麵，成日都好想食返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbca6a431ab811249bf8422974d0c2e0377ab5dd","tid":115275,"uid":41744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:40:13.000Z","msg":"京都豬一<br />\n三鳩亭"},{"pid":"522d445bc865934f5b4a94f7fd1e806ce13822c5","tid":115275,"uid":18394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T14:08:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0afcc59ee6152c54eed135ab61287fd12d405a74","tid":115275,"uid":48006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:07:43.000Z","msg":"清水寺附近 勝牛<br />\n<br />\nD相係老婆部手機到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  真心推介"},{"pid":"10e5c2afd4b1f79a12155f36b362630641fe08c6","tid":115275,"uid":41562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T01:49:34.000Z","msg":"六甲燒肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8204b8e7d028e38927cd60473a5137a614173dad","tid":115275,"uid":24069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T17:54:04.000Z","msg":"月尾去 留名<br />\n之前都係食國產牛"},{"pid":"2f656c4589709385bb3c7d